{"tid":1732124,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城online打boss]唔該可唔可以準備充足先出黎呀？？","createTime":"2019-11-17T23:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:06:54.000Z","uid":196446,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae204dc889d30cf18c66c5bc826d96160e7e76a","tid":1732124,"uid":196446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:22:50.000Z","msg":"今日！衣家！即刻！去買！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前線：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.頭盔</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.眼罩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.豬嘴</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.長傘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5.全黑包實自已</span><br />\n睇落好似好基本？我想講今日行動大部分企好前既都會缺1-2樣，得個豬嘴就衝，結果啲狗一放TG個個喊哂口咁退後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要企前，以上既裝備係必須！！！其他野等後一排幫你地帶啦好嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">中排：</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">1.豬嘴</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">2.眼罩</span><br />\n其實無喱兩樣野不如你唔好企咁中間啦，射一射又口水鼻涕流哂亂衝亂嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該 啲TG毒成咁就去買個豬嘴啦，成日平民口罩當神器！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">3.長傘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>4.火魔法原料</strong></span><br />\n中排可以幫手合成+帶料！然後比前排用，因為你地企個站好重要！火魔係最最最緊要！最好可以多到比前線狂掉亂掉都唔心痛果隻！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">後排/街坊：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">1.豬嘴</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">2.長傘</span><br />\n我真係求你地即刻去買啦！豬嘴係對自己最基本既保護黎架！企得後都會食到TG架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為左自己身體（由其係老弱街坊），唔該真係全民豬嘴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>3.火魔法原料x無限</strong></span><br />\n重點係，大家有無意過其實次次出黎鳩fingfing咁自己係應該擔當咩角色？<br />\n其實就係提供火魔原料呀！唔該，你地企後排既人佔全場起碼7成以上呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一人一支白電油都可以掟到前線手軟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該你地唔好再諗，今日起身即刻同我買5-6桶白電油+食用油+麵粉放屋企備用好唔好！！一有事就裝落啲水樽度帶2-3支出黎，每人2-3支夠整好多樽火魔法架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前線無限狂掟！你地後排就唔洗再避狗跑到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span>"},{"pid":"ca8d681643432456e579fce0bf88a46cc3c1b065","tid":1732124,"uid":196446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:23:45.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"da3a5ebc9b35d0f4dfed706ba34688e4a99c5571","tid":1732124,"uid":196446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:23:55.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"68d761ef075a22d6f3bba26e8894b0b568e77151","tid":1732124,"uid":196446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:24:06.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c46e3e4071ef96d40f54f6def75e99491a0c93ad","tid":1732124,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:24:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7c0bdb1e0395e8169d36c88f88ae7e11af02b758","tid":1732124,"uid":196446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:24:17.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"11b844d731c41df17a3d4288e1048bbb4d6f60a0","tid":1732124,"uid":196446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:24:47.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"16bd5fefb5e401bbb19720043c37963f9a985cd3","tid":1732124,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2278e966ad9a21daac440b0101bdfad5c280ba14","tid":1732124,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"